public org.springframework.hateoas.EntityModel<Doctor> newDoctor(@RequestBody @Valid

      • updateDoctor

        @PutMapping(value="/{doctorId}")
public org.springframework.hateoas.EntityModel<Doctor> updateDoctor(@PathVariable
                                                                                                     java.lang.Long doctorId,
                                                                                                     @RequestBody @Valid
                                                                                                     @Valid Doctor newDoctor)
        Handle the request to update the information of a Doctor Note: Every attribute of the Doctor is updated, even the Absence. If the Absence is missing, it will be deleted (if it exists)
        Parameters:
        doctorId - The id of the Doctor to update
        newDoctor - The values of newDoctor will be used to change the current Doctor
        Returns:
        The Doctor that has been persisted
